{"tid":1692093,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"原來艾堅遜以前係黑警","createTime":"2019-11-04T02:29:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-04T09:31:54.000Z","uid":179547,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"26c6d175e45a519e3faea1c1457d189f48c68e0b","tid":1692093,"uid":179547,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T02:29:44.000Z","msg":"前英超名哨卡頓保在一個專訪中談及現任的英超裁判，其中包括最近屢受爭議的馬田．艾堅遜。<br />\n<br />\nME and him fell out so I have not got really anything positive to say about him. I never really got on with him when I was in the Premier League and we never really saw eye to eye.<br />\n<br />\nThing is, he&rsquo;s an ex-copper &mdash; and he was that type of person on a football pitch. Off the pitch, in the group, I didn&rsquo;t integrate well with him, either.<br />\n<br />\nWhen I was fighting him for the Euros and the Champions League in 2016, he didn&rsquo;t like it when I got both finals.<br />\n<br />\nSorry, Martin.<br />\n<br />\n卡頓保：我跟他（艾堅遜）並不熟，對他我沒甚麼好話可說的。我還在英超時，跟他關係就沒好過，我們兩個從來沒看對眼。他以前是個警察，在球場上他也是那個類型的人。而在場下，在裁判圈子里，我也沒怎麼和他好好相處過。2016年我們兩個在歐聯和歐洲杯裡競爭很激烈，結果兩個決賽都歸我，這讓他很不爽。對不起了啊，馬丁。"},{"pid":"aecfd39afdca1657d47a1d2d978f4f6a0c00c030","tid":1692093,"uid":154872,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T02:51:57.000Z","msg":"卡頓保條仆街做球證做到好撚自負<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f8260e6059156a14905e37da03e92fb518ec8a4","tid":1692093,"uid":2949,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T02:53:36.000Z","msg":"邊個吹決賽原來都係競爭既一種"},{"pid":"62e18a984ba0025f365f95041a49cd847219fc08","tid":1692093,"uid":48222,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T02:53:56.000Z","msg":"英超球證除左米高奧利華都冇乜邊個係正常"},{"pid":"71c63e8c4bc2868ddd7d52bc568425fb5bbb309e","tid":1692093,"uid":199081,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T02:59:19.000Z","msg":"懷念韋比<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1f30bbbc6505ec1e1